### Create category - Players
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Players",
  "description": "Questions about FC Barcelona players."
}

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### Get category by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1

### Update category
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Players",
  "description": "Questions about legendary and current FC Barcelona players."
}

### Create duplicate category - should fail
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "players",
  "description": "Duplicate test."
}

### Create invalid category - empty name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Invalid category."
}

### Delete category
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1